languages.text: "Круг — это старшие агенты Миссии Касбаллики. Им уже известно, что я забрала жизнь Фалько, а скоро они услышат от меня, что я желаю забрать и его Торг. Но для этого мне потребуется их санкция".

"The circle are the high-ranking agents of the Kasballica Mission. They already know I took Falco's life, and they're about to hear that I want to take over his Trade — but for that, I need their approval."

languages.text: “他们是卡斯巴利卡犯罪集团的高阶代理人。他们已经知道我杀了法尔科，我准备告诉他们，说我打算接管法尔科的生意。不过在此之前，我需要先得到他们的批准。”
languages.original_text: "The circle are the high-ranking agents of the Kasballica Mission. They already know I took Falco's life, and they're about to hear that I want to take over his Trade — but for that, I need their approval."

traits.locale_text: “他们是卡斯巴利卡犯罪集团的高阶代理人。我打算向他们陈述我的诉求，接管法尔科的生意，但我需要先得到他们的批准。”
traits.speaker: JaeCompanion

languages.text: 「この団体さんは、カスバリカ聖務団の上級エージェント達さ。あたしがファルコの命を奪った事がもう耳に入っていて、ファルコの交易を引き継ぎたい意思を今から話すんだ…引き継ぎには、あの人達の承認が必要なんだよ」
languages.original_text: "The circle are the high-ranking agents of the Kasballica Mission. They already know I took Falco's life, and they're about to hear that I want to take over his Trade — but for that, I need their approval."

traits.speaker: JaeCompanion

languages.text: «El círculo está formado por los agentes de mayor rango de la misión Kasballica. Ya saben que maté a Falco y ahora van a enterarse de que quiero apoderarme del negocio de Falco, pero necesito su aprobación para ello».
languages.original_text: "The circle are the high-ranking agents of the Kasballica Mission. They already know I took Falco's life, and they're about to hear that I want to take over his Trade — but for that, I need their approval."

traits.locale_text: «Los agentes de mayor rango de la misión Kasballica. Voy a presentarles mi reclamación: quiero apoderarme del negocio de Falco, pero necesito su aprobación».
traits.speaker: JaeCompanion

languages.text: « Ce sont les agents les plus hauts placés de la Mission de la Kasballica. Ils savent déjà que j'ai pris la vie de Falco, et je vais leur annoncer mon intention de reprendre son commerce, mais pour ça, j'ai besoin de leur approbation. »
languages.original_text: "The circle are the high-ranking agents of the Kasballica Mission. They already know I took Falco's life, and they're about to hear that I want to take over his Trade — but for that, I need their approval."

traits.locale_text: « Ce sont les agents les plus hauts placés de la Mission de la Kasballica. Je dois leur faire part de mes revendications : je compte reprendre l'affaire de Falco, mais il me faut leur accord. »
traits.speaker: JaeCompanion

languages.text: "Der Kreis besteht aus den hochrangigen Agenten der Kasballica-Mission. Sie wissen bereits, dass ich Falcos Leben beendet habe und werden in Kürze erfahren, dass ich sein Geschäft übernehmen will ... aber dazu brauche ich ihre Zustimmung."
languages.original_text: "The circle are the high-ranking agents of the Kasballica Mission. They already know I took Falco's life, and they're about to hear that I want to take over his Trade — but for that, I need their approval."

languages.text: "Grup dediğim, Kasballica Misyonu'nun üst kademesindekiler. Falco'nun canını aldığımı zaten biliyorlar, onun Ticaretini devralmak istediğimi öğrenmek üzereler. Bunu yapmak için onların onayına ihtiyacım var."

traits.speaker: JaeCompanion
